https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/96rzOnJqjpMH9ZSBoMEfN2odDax.jpg Acclaimed actor and FDNY veteran Steve Buscemi looks at what it's like to work as a New York City firefighter. Utilizing exclusive behind-the-scenes footage and firsthand accounts from past and present firefighters, explore life in one of the world's most demanding fire departments while illuminating the lives of the often 'strong and silent' heroes. A Good Job: Stories of the FDNY
